description = "Emulator for the GameTank, an open-source 8-bit console by Clyde Shaffer built from twin WDC 65C02 CPUs (3.5MHz main + 14MHz audio coprocessor), a blitter-driven 128x128 framebuffer, and 2MB flash cartridges. Loads .gtr cartridges. Core emulation ported from the upstream GameTankEmulator."
